{"tid":948253,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【廣州十三行命案】亞姐亞軍老闆娘涉案 20歲倉務員疑遭掟落樓亡","createTime":"2018-12-20T02:02:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-20T06:45:12.000Z","uid":39464,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"4db8faab07be19d8dff43d6dde5cdf553bd2fe7a","tid":948253,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T02:02:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181219/large/1545234435_03b8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181219%2Flarge%2F1545234435_03b8.jpg&h=1da86d15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地服裝批發市場「廣州十三行」本月16日，一名20歲黃姓青年在鬧市，倒臥在血泊之中身亡。據一名死者相熟的林姓友人在微信上爆料，涉案老闆娘質疑青年監守自盜，聯同男友及4名打手，將青年押上9樓痛毆2小時，打至半死後，再在露台推他下樓，全程只需動口不動手，並披露主使命案的老闆娘為上屆亞洲小姐亞軍許靜；保住她的男友亦來頭甚猛，為香港女星劉嘉玲廣州本色酒吧的股東，更傳他有黑社會、軍方背景。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181219/large/1545233624_9830.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181219%2Flarge%2F1545233624_9830.jpg&h=3d2f97f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n紅圈為許靜及其41歲男友。<br />\n<br />\n網上爆料人士透露，32歲的許靜經營的淘寶店，名為「許想想女裝批發工廠」，以她作為法人代表在工商註冊登記的公司名稱為「廣州千熹服飾有限公司」。此外，許靜在其微博＠M許想想中，自我介紹為亞洲小姐廣東省亞軍、原創設計師。而公開資料顯示，許靜確為2017年的亞洲小姐廣州賽區獲得過亞軍。<br />\n<br />\n許靜原來早有「黑歷史」。天眼查顯示，該公司因登記地址，已於今年7月3日被廣州海珠區工商部門列入「經營異常名錄」。另外，網傳的傳單形容許靜為「欠工錢不還的『東北女』」，內容指控「欠工錢遲遲不給，你們心裏就不虛嗎，還叫你男人去工廠威脅老人，說我們再鬧就小心家裏小孩，你們做生意就這樣欺負工廠的嗎？」，怒斥她「無信用，不講理，失品德」。網上亦曝光了許靜的身份證，顯示她於1986年7月17日出生，32歲，出身哈爾濱。<br />\n<br />\n許靜可在光天化日下作案，可見她勢力強勁。有網民分析，許靜在十三行開店，肯定財源滾滾；其次她還是個亞洲小姐，可算是個一、二線的網紅；第三她能找到黑社會的人，說明有人保護，網傳她的男朋友是廣州本色酒吧的股東之一，更為了她買通派出所，讓家屬簽名確認案件為自殺案。<br />\n<br />\n警方初步調查報告指出，黃男死者的死因是「高（處）墜（下）」。不過，死者家屬認為，黃男被圍毆至半殘，當時根本無法站立，哪有可能自行跨越欄杆墮樓，因此懷疑黃男是被人抱起掉下樓致死，懷疑警方將案件列為自殺案，掩飾案件的刑事成份。數十名死者家屬周一（17日）到當地派出所門外，拉起橫額示威，促警方徹查事件。死者胞兄亦在派出所門口拍片，稱黃男生前遭多人毆打近2小時，質問警方是否有調查此事。警方於周一深夜公佈，包括許靜等6名涉案人士被刑事拘留。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181220/59047634\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181220%2F59047634&d=bxRmApblJ2GFsDTLoFA1iywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=23e6fc8c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181220%2F59047634&h=1e35efd5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181220/59047634</a><br />\n<br />\n警稱「掟落樓」係謠言 網民：良心不會痛嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181219/large/1545232533_fcb8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181219%2Flarge%2F1545232533_fcb8.jpg&h=7e3891eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地服裝批發市場「廣州十三行」本月16日發生命案。一名20歲黃姓青年在鬧市中墮樓死亡。涉案老闆娘、前亞姐許靜疑是主使殺手將黃男毒打、掟下樓的幕後黑手。死者家屬在警處外申冤的影片在網上流傳。另一邊廂，警方起初通報案情時，只將事件列為一般墮樓案處理，引來網民質疑不公正。警方持續匯報事件，昨晚近9時稱，「死者被毆打並被扔下樓屬謠言」，同一時間，許靜的微博、抖音在清空，令網民不寒而慄，懷疑警方欲就此丟淡事件，質問辦案警方「良心不會痛嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n警情昨晚通報稱，警方高度重視16日於一德路大同坊北座9樓，20歲男子黃X墮樓案件，已成立由市、區兩級公安機關相關部門組成的專案組，全力開展偵查工作。通報並稱，連日來，微博、微信群等自媒體平台傳播所謂「死者被毆打並被扔下樓」的質疑，經警方調查，為死者同事林X在其朋友圈發佈的不實信息，林X已承認錯誤，並在朋友圈澄清；而有關「死者黃X被女老闆毆打」等影片，經黃男父親辨認，影片中的當事人並非其子。<br />\n<br />\n此外，針對網絡流傳「買通派出所讓家屬簽名確認是自殺」的說法，廣州警方鄭重聲明為純屬謠言，將依法追究造謠者的法律責任。<br />\n<br />\n不過，網民都不滿意警方的交代，質問「被刑拘？就在剛剛嫌疑人許某微博被人清空，還改了名，怎解釋？」、「謠言？為甚麼急着刪微博？作賊心虛？」、「到底真相是甚麼大家心知肚明，在這玩文字游戲？收錢收傻了？」、「可怕，不知道發這條通報的警員心裏是不是也在罵」、「還事發當天就高度重視，要臉麼？」、「都不問問你們自己，為啥相信謠言都不相信你們」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181220/59048740\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181220%2F59048740&d=bxRmApblJ2GFsDTLoFA1iywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=adcce64d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181220%2F59048740&h=1e6307de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181220/59048740</a>"},{"pid":"45b0d5bd38532d92c9a2589bf42aeec1d4f16769","tid":948253,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T02:03:57.000Z","msg":"咪又係為賠錢"},{"pid":"5c3e3d4b74a65a545d2101f5c9f915250b9bb286","tid":948253,"uid":90820,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T02:16:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>警方初步調查報告指出，黃男死者的死因是「高（處）墜（下）」</blockquote><br />\n中國真係好興乜柒都簡稱"},{"pid":"b6820980bd5d57e8a1b3c26b9c03cc6e0900e4b1","tid":948253,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T02:20:20.000Z","msg":"WHO"},{"pid":"c80571f90dc8a01bc65190c82ce30b49e2442db5","tid":948253,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T02:20:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4b0a02198e2984eae85de1e1d02d0343735b0ea","tid":948253,"uid":156363,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T02:35:21.000Z","msg":"東北人出名乜都郁左手先"},{"pid":"d0c73b8e21ae9b655b1a7565d2475254f8ab8ba5","tid":948253,"uid":50610,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T03:05:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Nn8pkCZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNn8pkCZ.png&h=b0edf51b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0b6c1f719a471c1f8fa4dc4f69fff788c59ef632","tid":948253,"uid":133529,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"45b0d5bd38532d92c9a2589bf42aeec1d4f16769","tid":948253,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T02:03:57.000Z","msg":"咪又係為賠錢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T03:10:58.000Z","msg":"來，你跟我番大陸一轉，我掟你落街，之後賠返錢俾你。睇你都係值得果十幾廿蚊港幣，我賠得起<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d1205e5b05da152881d6f7c0cf2535c4b2e81f0","tid":948253,"uid":33643,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"45b0d5bd38532d92c9a2589bf42aeec1d4f16769","tid":948253,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T02:03:57.000Z","msg":"咪又係為賠錢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T03:28:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">收皮啦臭串連登乞衣&mdash;EDO脆餅#23833</span><br />\n<br />\n(被追擊後第&ldquo;6&rdquo;個新名<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 儲錢要供824（<span style=\"color: red;\">連我名都抄埋</span>））</span><br />\n<br />\n想買不死鳥風褸，點買先最抵？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/504716/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/504716/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n乞衣仔經典語錄:<br />\n&rdquo;<em><span style=\"color: blue;\">我：你食撚左飯未<br />\n你： 我食左屎啦 </span></em>&ldquo;<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n臭串想反追擊但話左自己係on9仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q5KSy5P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ5KSy5P.jpg&h=6e9db0dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong></strong><br />\n<br />\n垃圾乞衣仔你上水未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9c7dd8fde03b9b2d356020dc1ebac3c9f6e6a7e","tid":948253,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T03:29:40.000Z","msg":"嘩屌<br />\n濃妝整容妖怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5177e9dff5ccb902d7bd992c4c80f0efb157191e","tid":948253,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T05:53:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/SW3u4ZjHzWo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FSW3u4ZjHzWo&d=bxRmApblJ2GFsDTLoFA1iywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=6a3d9d7c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/SW3u4ZjHzWo</a>"},{"pid":"31193afb71bccd68cb1c85ca9634269d90066c6c","tid":948253,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T05:53:31.000Z","msg":"我估會好似沙地記者卡舒吉被殺案咁,上面最大粒果個話自己乜都唔知,搵D細嘅認頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed6373a1ddf64153eb630c19644f19f07c291047","tid":948253,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T05:54:14.000Z","msg":"亞視執左都仲可以有亞姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e813d2ad719a1b3272f6f0540ae3a2dab07695ce","tid":948253,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed6373a1ddf64153eb630c19644f19f07c291047","tid":948253,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T05:54:14.000Z","msg":"亞視執左都仲可以有亞姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T05:56:10.000Z","msg":"開返啦...用盒睇"},{"pid":"137fa96c68463cbd9e4d21f292f6bfbb33ed190a","tid":948253,"uid":56212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d0c73b8e21ae9b655b1a7565d2475254f8ab8ba5","tid":948253,"uid":50610,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T03:05:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Nn8pkCZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNn8pkCZ.png&h=b0edf51b&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T06:01:27.000Z","msg":"古惑仔嘅烏鴉同耀揚其實都幾多金句"},{"pid":"dc642670bf6c079c423f952e24f6c1e4d2951cdc","tid":948253,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T06:45:12.000Z","msg":"好彩死果個唔太出名 乜事都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}